works.description: We have earlier seen a range of scale marvels from the Ferrari Store, which show no signs of deviation from the real ones when it comes to replication. Some of the examples include a F10 Fernando Alonso version, a Ferrari 250 California Spyder SWB of 1960 and the Ferrari 458 Italia. Detailed enough to impress auto enthusiasts (especially Ferrari fans) and collectors, here is yet another offering from the store - a limited edition 1:8 scale model of the Motorboat Arno XI.
